   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Environmental Diplomacy for Indonesian Youth</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will train Indonesian youth in the North Maluku region (eastern Indonesia) to become effective change-makers in their communities to address critical regional environmental issues, including climate change, plastic pollution, and air quality.  Through digital communication technologies and realistic scientific simulations, participants will role-play as policy makers and diverse stakeholders negotiating global environmental challenges, then apply those lessons in real life.</narrative>
  </description>
